        <http://qudt.org/vocab/unit/MicroJ>,
        <http://qudt.org/vocab/unit/MilliJ>,
        <http://qudt.org/vocab/unit/PetaJ>,
        <http://qudt.org/vocab/unit/PlanckEnergy>,
