        <http://qudt.org/vocab/unit/IN-PER-SEC>,
        <http://qudt.org/vocab/unit/KN>,
        <http://qudt.org/vocab/unit/KiloM-PER-DAY>,
        <http://qudt.org/vocab/unit/KiloM-PER-HR>,
