        <http://qudt.org/vocab/unit/SolarMass>,
        <http://qudt.org/vocab/unit/Stone_UK>,
        <http://qudt.org/vocab/unit/TONNE>,
        <http://qudt.org/vocab/unit/TON_Assay>,
        <http://qudt.org/vocab/unit/TON_LONG>,
