        <http://qudt.org/vocab/unit/EV>,
        <http://qudt.org/vocab/unit/E_h>,
        <http://qudt.org/vocab/unit/ExaJ>,
        <http://qudt.org/vocab/unit/FT-LB_F>,
        <http://qudt.org/vocab/unit/FT-PDL>,
