        <http://qudt.org/vocab/unit/KiloV-A-HR>,
        <http://qudt.org/vocab/unit/KiloV-A_Reactive-HR>,
        <http://qudt.org/vocab/unit/KiloW-HR>,
        <http://qudt.org/vocab/unit/MegaEV>,
        <http://qudt.org/vocab/unit/MegaJ>,
