        <http://qudt.org/vocab/unit/GigaW-HR>,
        <http://qudt.org/vocab/unit/J>,
        <http://qudt.org/vocab/unit/KiloBTU_IT>,
        <http://qudt.org/vocab/unit/KiloBTU_TH>,
        <http://qudt.org/vocab/unit/KiloCAL>,
